## 📊 Key Schema Design Decisions

| Feature | Schema Implementation | Rationale |
|---------|----------------------|-----------|
| **Operation Routing** | `parameters.oneOf` with `if/then` conditions | Enables strict type-validation per pipeline stage while keeping a single unified payload format. |
| **Anthropomorphic Mapping** | `limb_adaptation`, `facial_rig_tolerance`, `expressive_overrides` | Explicitly handles non-human topology constraints while preserving lip-sync and emotional articulation. |
| **Acoustic Design** | `harmonic_layers`, `sub_bass_resonance`, `spectral_filters` | Provides programmatic control over mythological/non-human timbres beyond standard TTS. |
| **Compliance & Provenance** | `clone_consent_hash` (SHA-256), `embed_c2pa`, `accuracy_legend` | Enforces legal/ethical gates at the CLI level, not just the UI. |
| **Accessibility** | `wcag_compliance_level`, `audio_description`, `captions_vtt` | Bakes WCAG 2.2 standards into the export pipeline by default. |
| **Execution Modes** | `sync`, `async`, `dry_run` | Supports CI/CD testing, heavy cloud GPU queues, and rapid local validation. |

